data.text:
.v3_demo-hero-testimonials {
  width: 100%;
  max-width: 42rem;
  margin: 4rem auto 0 auto;
}

.v3_demo-hero .v3_demo-hero-testimonials {
  margin-top: 0 !important;
}

.v3_demo-flows .swiper-slide {
  text-align: center;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
}

.v3_demo-hero-testimonials-wrapper {
  width: 120%;
  transform: translateX(-10%);
  padding: 0 12%;
  position: relative;
  z-index: -2;
  mask-image: linear-gradient(to right, transparent 0%, black 15%, black 85%, transparent 100%);
}

.v3_demo-hero-testimonials-pagination {
  display: flex;
  grid-column-gap: 0.5rem;
}

.v3_demo-hero-testimonials-pagination span.swiper-pagination-bullet {
  width: 14px;
  height: 14px;
  border-radius: 50%;
  border: 1px solid rgba(28, 25, 23, 0.8);
  background: transparent;
  margin: 0 !important;
  padding: 0 !important;
}

.v3_demo-hero-testimonials-pagination span.swiper-pagination-bullet.swiper-pagination-bullet-active {
  background: var(--v3-colors--v3-orange-700);
  border-color: var(--v3-colors--v3-orange-700);
}

/* Made pagination left aligned on desktop for Get Started page's Demo Hero testimonials */
@media screen and (min-width: 992px) {
  .v3_demo-hero-content .v3_demo-hero-testimonials-pagination {
    justify-content: flex-start;
  }
}


/* >> Mobile styles */

@media screen and (max-width: 991px) {

  .v3_demo-flows .v3_demo-hero-testimonials {
    margin: 4rem auto 0 auto;
  }

}

@media screen and (max-width: 767px) {

  .v3_demo-hero-testimonials-pagination span.swiper-pagination-bullet {
 	 	width: 12px;
  	height: 12px;			
  }

}

We had many issues with TaxJar, including incorrect tax filings that resulted in an overpayment of $5,700 and non-existent customer support. Numeral provided complete onboarding, prompt customer service, and rapid feature additions based on customer input.Kevin Chanthasiriphan,Founder, immiI was spending way too many hours every month on sales tax. Numeral has made it easy to identify and know the tax laws. And then, on your behalf, registering and managing everything takes the worry off my plate.Jesse Hiss,Founder, Fresh SendsIt's set it and forget it. At the end of the day, I'd much rather spend time growing our business than worrying about sales tax. We love Numeral. I don't know how you squeeze a number out of it, but I'd give working with them a 10 out of 10.Adrian Zhang,Co-founder, The WooblesAs a founder, sales tax for my SaaS business was the last thing I wanted to think about. Numeral made it dead simple for Archive to stay compliant across multiple jurisdictions. Plus, their developer experience is thoughtful and built with craft.Paul Benigeri,CEO, ArchiveNumeral tailors its solution to each client’s needs. Everything is customized. And I loved that I could talk to sales tax experts. Numeral guarantees no compliance mistakes will happen. Nobody else was willing to make that promise.Jason Wong,Founder, Doe LashesSales tax compliance is a consistent frustration for my Series A & B SaaS clients. As a busy CFO, I want to spend my energy on strategic work, not compliance. With Numeral, I can delegate away the minutia of state tax compliance.Hari Seshadri,CEO, Fractional

